dct_title_s: Carte de la Baye de Trinquemale.
dct_description_sm: Cartographic Details: Scale not given. (E 81°08'34"--E 81°20'01"/N 8°40'38"--N 8°27'09"). Nautical chart showing fortifications, bays, and islands within Trincomalee Bay. Relief shown by hachures and landforms. Depths shown by soundings. Oriented with north to the lower right. Likely extracted from Abbeá Prevost's L'Histoire generale des voyages."Suppl. au Tome VIII Number 7"--Lower left margin. Includes illustrations. In French.
Ames Library of South Asia Maps
dcat_keyword_sm: Trincomalee (Sri Lanka) Maps Early Works to 1800
